About Me

I help companies ship products fast without compromising quality.

I've spent the last decade building products for the world's top tech companies. Today, I partner with founders to bring their ideas to life. As a design partner, I will:

  • Help you define your product strategy without slowing you down
  • Quickly create high-fidelity interactive prototypes to validate ideas
  • Collaborate directly with engineering teams to launch swiftly
  • Build and nurture a design team that's set up for success
View resume →

Approach

01. Shared ownership

Whenever I work, I collaborate deeply as an integral part of your team, ensuring we're moving the process forward together.

02. I work fast. I mean like really fast.

Quick iteration allows us to learn through rapid prototyping and get to a great UI extremely fast.

03. Show and tell

I frequently share work in progress, usually in the form of screen recordings via Loom.
